==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roughshod
<hw>Rough"shod</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Shod with shoes
armed with points or calks; <as>as, a <ex>roughshod</ex>
horse</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To ride roughshod</b></col>, <cd>to pursue a course
regardless of the pain or distress it may cause others.</cd></cs> <--
usu. with "over" -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roughstrings</ent>⟦br⟧
